net.floodlightcontroller.debugevent

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.floodlightcontroller.debugevent.Event

  • public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic Event class used to store different categories of events. DebugEventService uses this class to store each Event instance. Each DebugEventService.EventCategory has a different object of type EventClass. This is used internally for all DebugEvent processing. For display via REST and CLI, it is transformed to EventResource object.
